{
  "stem": "1222.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He's in Israel now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was Monek Averbuch, older with two years than me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The other follow was alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He runned away probably while he was walking to the grave, there on the way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These two boys were city boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I never knew them before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They couldn't talk too good in Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It helped me, because I grew up between Ukrainian in the village.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So we start [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So up till today, one of them, Monek Averbuch, said to me, Schmilic, my-- let's go to the police station.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they are going to kill us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said to him, you know what, Shmonek?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SOBBING] Life has got to go on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe God saved us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have to see what we could do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So up till today, when I'm in Israel, many times, when I come over there, he-- the man is over 6 foot.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His wife always says to him-- to me, you know, Schmilic, I live with my-- my husband for years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never saw Monek crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Each time when you come to Israel, he kicks me out of the bed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he wants to sleep with you, and he always cries.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He remembers the days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What we went through together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Unfortunately, that didn't take two weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's a whole saying, three's a crowd, two's companies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we used to go-- day-- day time we used to hide itself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It shows right there on the picture that I showed it to you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to hide in the straw, digging out in the straw [INAUDIBLE] day time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At nighttime, we used to go to steal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How we used to steal?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Summertime was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
